title: Soap and Foam - Self Proclaimed Geniuses (2008).uh_yay
description:
Soap and Foam is the collective effort of Abhilash and Tanmay Buch. We are pleased to offer you "Soap and Foam - Self Proclaimed Geniuses," completely free online.  We have one goal and that is to make quality music for true lovers of music.  There is no bullshit here; we don&#039;t want to make a dime.  We just want people to experience that which is Soap and Foam.

Enjoy.

Soap and Foam
